and what you desire,

254
00:17:56,767 --> 00:17:59,967
but this… is some sisterly devotion.

255
00:18:00,633 --> 00:18:04,200
I didn't know you badly wanted
a little brother.

256
00:18:04,266 --> 00:18:05,700
Oh, stop it.

257
00:18:07,433 --> 00:18:09,533
