312
00:22:19,133 --> 00:22:22,500
I don't know about that,
but I'll certainly try.

313
00:22:22,567 --> 00:22:24,834
Wow. You're well-spoken.

314
00:22:24,900 --> 00:22:26,600
Oh, no. Not really.

315
00:22:28,900 --> 00:22:31,300
Se-yeon, where should I work?

316
