00:30:43,934 --> 00:30:45,433
Let's drink up!

445
00:30:46,133 --> 00:30:49,266
You, me, and my siblings.

446
00:30:50,133 --> 00:30:53,934
Jerks who grow up with plenty are selfish.

447
00:30:54,567 --> 00:30:55,900
